programme.title: Cells At Work! Code Black, Ep 1
programme.desc: Humans are complex biological robots that are made up of trillion of cells, each with their own structure and function. Even a single cell cannot slack off. Scientists have come a long way in estimating the number of cells in the average human body. According to the most recent estimates, the number of cells in a human body is around 30 trillion. Hataraku Saibou Black is about a fight of these 30 trillion cells against the bad habits of the owner of the body to keep him alive.

programme.title: Forever And Ever

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Lo Wei mengarahkan film romantis yang menampilkan bakat akting Ivy Ling Po nan luar biasa. Film ini bercerita tentang seorang sarjana muda yang diperdaya untuk menikahi seorang putri bangsawan.

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: Seorang biksu gila menghadapi cendekiawan legendaris yang berubah menjadi jin, Lu Tung Pin. Keduanya menyebabkan kekacauan saat bersaing satu sama lain, baik dalam kesenangan, sihir, wanita, atau senjata!

programme.title: The Shaolin Avengers
programme.desc: Heroism and romance combine in this action-packed martial arts classic. When the Shaolin are betrayed by the White-Browed Hermit, hotheaded warrior-hero Fong Sai Yuk vows revenge.

programme.title: The Shaolin Avengers
programme.desc: Aksi kepahlawanan dan kisah asmara mewarnai film seni bela diri klasik ini. Saat Shaolin dikhianati oleh Pertapa Alis Putih, Fong Sai Yuk sang prajurit pemarah bersumpah untuk membalas dendam.

programme.title: Somewhere Winter
programme.desc: The film follows the love story of a university student, An Ran and a Taiwanese man, Qi Xiao. They met and fell in love with each other in Beijing in 1991, at a concert by Chyi Chin, a Taiwanese singer.

programme.title: Somewhere Winter
programme.desc: Film ini menampilkan kisah cinta seorang mahasiswa bernama An Ran dan seorang pria Taiwan, Qi Xiao. Mereka bertemu dan saling jatuh cinta di Beijing pada tahun 1991, di konser Chyi Chin, seorang penyanyi Taiwan.

programme.title: Septet: The Story Of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: Septet: The Story Of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Untuk pertama kalinya, tujuh sutradara dengan gaya nan unik dan paling dihormati di Hong Kong berkumpul guna menciptakan serangkaian kisah tentang kota Hong Kong dari tahun 50-an hingga masa kini.

programme.title: The Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ip Man takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tian's daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond.

programme.title: The Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ip Man menerima sebuah tantangan bertarung dari master asal utara yang sudah tua bernama Gong Yu Tian dan berhasil memenangkannya. Namun, ia dikalahkan oleh putri sang master, Gong Er, dan jatuh cinta padanya.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: Chen An si pembunuh bersumpah akan membalas kematian saudarinya yang dibunuh oleh suatu geng. Pertarungan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan pun dimulai saat ia berurusan dengan polisi dan triad secara bersamaan!

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs and seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU to find his lost revolver. Ho and his team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: Sersan Lo Sa meminta bantuan Sersan Mike Ho dari PTU untuk menemukan senjatanya yang dirampas oleh empat pemuda triad. Mereka hanya memiliki waktu hingga fajar untuk menemukannya dan membersihkan kekacauan tersebut.

programme.title: Special Couple
programme.desc: Gu disguising as a couple with Jin to secure his stay in London. Everything goes well until Gu falls for his neighbour, Hermione, and Jin's parents pay a surprise visit.

programme.title: Special Couple
programme.desc: Gu dan Jin menyamar sebagai pasangan demi mengamankan masa tinggal Gu di London. Semua berjalan lancar hingga Gu jatuh cinta pada tetangganya, Hermione, dan kedua orang tua Jin datang berkunjung secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: David Ki, one of the top rock climbers in Asia, lost everything when a motorcycle accident took away his ability to walk. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found his own way of scaling the dizzying peaks again.

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: David Ki, salah satu pemanjat tebing terkenal di Asia, kehilangan segalanya saat sebuah kecelakaan menghilangkan kemampuannya untuk berjalan. Pantang menyerah, David menemukan caranya sendiri untuk kembali mendaki.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: Berdasarkan kisah nyata sepasang suami istri, film ini bercerita tentang perjalanan seorang suami melintasi kampung halaman mereka di Selandia Baru menuju sejumlah tempat yang bermakna bagi mendiang istri tercintanya.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: Yum, a detective agency that handles supernatural cases, investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building. They discover that the spirits are created so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: Sebuah kantor detektif yang menangani kasus supranatural, Yum, menyelidiki sejumlah roh jahat di suatu bangunan tua dan mendapati bahwa roh-roh itu diciptakan guna mengosongkan bangunan agar dapat dibangun kembali.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police that ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Ho datang ke Hong Kong sebagai imigran gelap pada tahun 1963 dan membangun kerajaan di dunia rahasia para pengedar narkoba dan polisi korup yang memerintah kota di bawah kekuasaan detektif terkenal bernama Lee Rock.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: Sebelum benar-benar menikah, seorang wanita Hong Kong yang baru bertunangan mencoba melepaskan diri dari sebuah pernikahan palsu rahasia dengan seorang pria yang membayarnya bertahun-tahun lalu.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Gambler
programme.desc: Ho Sheung-Sang dan Manfred, dua individu yang kecanduan judi dan sering menghabiskan waktu mereka di kasino. Mereka bertemu dalam situasi yang tidak terduga dan dengan cepat menemukan kesamaan dalam kecanduan mereka. Cinta pun tumbuh di antara mereka, dan mereka memutuskan untuk menikah. Namun, kehidupan pernikahan mereka tidaklah mudah. Kecanduan judi membawa mereka ke dalam serangkaian masalah finansial yang serius. Utang mereka semakin menumpuk, dan tekanan dari para penagih utang mulai menghantui kehidupan sehari-hari mereka. Dalam upaya untuk mengatasi situasi ini, mereka mencoba berbagai cara yang konyol dan kreatif untuk mendapatkan uang, termasuk ikut serta dalam berbagai kompetisi dan bahkan melakukan penipuan kecil-kecilan.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixâ€™s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixâ€™s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Enter The Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fiancÃ© left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Teenage Dreamers
programme.desc: This refreshing musical comedy tempers its fizzy charm with just enough tartness to insure its charming buoyancy. This light look at teenage life even won starlet Chou Hsiu-lan a Hong Kong Film Awards nomination for Best Newcomer.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: Two Tigers is a crime comedy movie about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman, Zhang Cheng Gong, for ransom.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: Two Tigers adalah sebuah film komedi kriminal tentang seorang pria muda, Fang Nan, yang menculik seorang pengusaha paruh baya, Zhang Cheng Gong, untuk mendapatkan uang tebusan.

programme.title: The Brotherhood Of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: When radio frequencies used by rebel forces from Chinese Civil War disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: Saat frekuensi radio yang digunakan oleh para pemberontak Perang Saudara Tiongkok menghilang, Agen Zhang meminta bantuan seorang penyetem piano dengan pendengaran istimewa untuk menemukan sinyal transmisi mereka.

programme.title: One And Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubâ€™s top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Once In A Blue Moon
programme.desc: Mei-chun longs to reunite with her estranged father, her brother conceals his separation from his wife, and their mother harbors guilt over her husband's past departure. Can this troubled family overcome secrets and reconcile?

programme.title: Once In A Blue Moon
programme.desc: Mei-chun ingin bersatu kembali dengan ayahnya yang telah lama berpisah, saudara laki-lakinya menyembunyikan perpisahannya dengan istrinya, dan ibu mereka menyimpan rasa bersalah atas kepergian suaminya di masa lalu. Bisakah keluarga yang bermasalah ini mengatasi rahasia dan berdamai?

programme.title: Tales From Occult: Body & Soul
programme.desc: This horror anthology series returns to feature three spooky crime stories about an ex-hair model, a cat lover and the love triangle between a dental nurse, a dentist and a chef.

programme.title: Tales From Occult: Body & Soul
programme.desc: Serial antologi horor ini kembali menampilkan tiga kisah kriminal nan menyeramkan tentang seorang mantan model rambut, pencinta kucing, dan cinta segitiga antara seorang perawat gigi, dokter gigi, dan koki.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: An urban sketcher suffering from ALS wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. Then, he asks his old classmate to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Seorang seniman yang menderita ALS ingin memilki kenangan indah karena kondisinya kian memburuk. Ia pun meminta sang mantan teman sekelas untuk memenuhi keinginan terakhirnya dengan menjadi kekasihnya selama satu hari.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Chinese Feng Shui master, Carson was a 'Natural Born Player', taking names and breaking hearts. Fate had it that he would meet his match, the hot veterinarian, Chi-Ling.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Chinese Feng Shui master, Carson was a 'Natural Born Player', taking names and breaking hearts. Fate had it that he would meet his match, the hot veterinarian, Chi-Ling.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Pakar Feng Shui Tiongkok, Carson adalah 'Playboy Sejati' yang kerap membuat wanita patah hati. Takdir lalu mempertemukannya dengan lawan yang seimbang, seorang dokter hewan nan seksi bernama Chi-Ling.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Pakar Feng Shui Tiongkok, Carson adalah 'Playboy Sejati' yang kerap membuat wanita patah hati. Takdir lalu mempertemukannya dengan lawan yang seimbang, seorang dokter hewan nan seksi bernama Chi-Ling.

programme.title: Let's Make Laugh
programme.desc: Security guard Lee Go is assigned to keep guard at a house while the owner is away. However, a series of hilarious misunderstandings occur.

programme.title: Let's Make Laugh
programme.desc: Satpam Lee Go ditugaskan untuk menjaga sebuah rumah saat pemiliknya pergi. Namun, serangkaian kesalahpahaman lucu terjadi.

programme.title: Princess And 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters must defeat the enemy and save a warlord who refuses to side with the Japanese enemies.

programme.title: Princess And 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Tujuh ahli Kung Fu harus mengalahkan musuh dan menyelamatkan seorang panglima perang yang menolak berpihak pada musuh Jepang.

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Chan Tin Mei (Sammi Cheng) and Ho Bun (Alan Luk)'s son passes away abruptly at just three years old due to congenital heart disease. Suffering in unfathomable pain over the loss, Mei resists having another child. One day, Mei finds out that they can become a foster family.

programme.title: Once In A Blue Moon
programme.desc: Mei-chun longs to reunite with her estranged father, her brother conceals his separation from his wife, and their mother harbors guilt over her husband's past departure. Can this troubled family overcome secrets and reconcile?

programme.title: Once In A Blue Moon
programme.desc: Mei-chun ingin bersatu kembali dengan ayahnya yang telah lama berpisah, saudara laki-lakinya menyembunyikan perpisahannya dengan istrinya, dan ibu mereka menyimpan rasa bersalah atas kepergian suaminya di masa lalu. Bisakah keluarga yang bermasalah ini mengatasi rahasia dan berdamai?

programme.title: Customs Frontline
programme.desc: Hong Kong customs officers discover illegal weapons on a cargo ship and trace them back to an international conflict. Elite agents go undercover, uncovering a transnational operation with roots closer to home.

programme.title: Customs Frontline
programme.desc: Petugas bea cukai Hong Kong menemukan senjata ilegal di sebuah kapal kargo dan melacaknya hingga ke konflik internasional. Agen elit menyamar, mengungkap operasi transnasional yang berakar di dekat rumah.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Bowen yang dulunya adalah seorang bankir sukses, kini menghabiskan malamnya di restoran cepat saji 24 jam, tempat ia bertemu dengan sekelompok tunawisma. Mereka pun bersama-sama berjuang memperbaiki hidup mereka.

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evaâ€™s mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her motherâ€™s wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evaâ€™s heart?

programme.title: Imprisoned 2: No Escape
programme.desc: Jake, mantan narapidana yang berusaha menjalani hidup normal setelah keluar dari penjara. Namun, masa lalunya yang kelam kembali menghantuinya ketika seorang musuh lama, yang ia kira telah lama hilang, muncul kembali dengan rencana balas dendam yang mematikan. Jake diculik dan dibawa ke fasilitas penahanan rahasia yang jauh lebih brutal dan tidak dapat ditembus dibandingkan penjara sebelumnya. Pertempuran hidup dan mati dengan sesama tahanan menjadi perjuangan untuk bertahan hidup disana. Pengawasan ketat dan manipulasi dari pihak pengelola penjara pun menjadi satu tantangan.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Ming is a mole in the police department and Yan is a police mole in the Triads. Leading parallel lives, Ming and Yan are feeling increasingly trapped in their false surroundings and they're desperate to find a way out.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Ming menyusupi kepolisian atas suruhan triad, sementara Yan adalah polisi yang menyamar sebagai anggota triad. Menjalani kehidupan ganda membuat keduanya merasa terjebak dalam kebohongan dan ingin mencari jalan keluar.

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: a film crew is haunted by a ghost, a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, and a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall.

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: Film ini terdiri dari tiga cerita hantu, yaitu seorang kru film yang diganggu oleh hantu, seorang sopir taksi yang mengajak kekasihnya berlibur, dan sesosok hantu anak-anak yang menolak untuk meninggalkan mal.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Berlatar di tahun 2020 saat wabah COVID-19, film ini menampilkan sejumlah kisah yang saling berhubungan dalam kehidupan tiga wanita saat menjalani masa depan yang tak pasti di antara teman-teman dan keluarga mereka.

programme.title: The Flying Mr. B
programme.desc: Mr. B, yang memiliki nama lengkap Benjamin Barker, adalah seorang pegawai kantoran yang menjalani kehidupan monoton. Suatu hari, dalam sebuah insiden aneh di laboratorium ilmiah tempat temannya bekerja, Mr. B terpapar dengan zat misterius yang memberinya kemampuan untuk terbang. Awalnya, dia merasa bingung dan takut, tetapi segera dia mulai mengeksplorasi kekuatan barunya dengan penuh semangat.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The 'passion choir pilot program' trains students from three underperforming schools' choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: Film ini berkisah tentang program 'passion choir pilot' yang melatih para siswa anggota paduan suara dari tiga sekolah dengan kinerja buruk untuk berpartisipasi dalam sebuah kompetisi paduan suara antarsekolah.

programme.title: The Hatching

programme.title: The Bird Catcher

programme.title: Time Is Up

programme.title: The Canyons

programme.title: Kiko
programme.desc: Kiko, seekor anak ikan mas koki yang sangat mandiri, walaupun ia anak tunggal. programme.title: Kiko
programme.desc: Kiko tells of a child of a goldfish who is very independent, even though he is an only child. Kiko who is always cheerful has four good friends, namely Lola the discus fish, Ting Ting the crab, Patino the catfish and Poli the betta fish. On the other hand, the antagonists, Karkus the catfish and Pupus the eel, always make Kiko's life chaotic. One day, the lake where Kiko lives is polluted due to the reckless acts of humans, causing Kiko and friends to turn into mutants.

programme.title: Jelly Jamm S1, Ep 40
programme.desc: Jelly Jamm takes place on a fictional, colourful planet called Jammbo, following the adventures of seven characters: Bello, Goomo, Rita, Mina, Ongo, the King, and the Queen, who live in a small neighbourhood there. The planet has a music factory where all of the music in the universe originates from and is produced continuously through bubbles. If the music produced by the factory had stopped, time on Jammbo would also stop, causing the characters to freeze. Each episode features a plot in which a character or multiple characters learn a teachable lesson which the viewers can learn from, and features an insert song which may be instrumental or vocal.

programme.title: Jelly Jamm S1, Ep 40
programme.desc: Jelly Jamm terjadi di planet fiksi penuh warna bernama Jammbo, mengikuti petualangan tujuh karakter: Bello, Goomo, Rita, Mina, Ongo, Raja, dan Ratu, yang tinggal di lingkungan kecil di sana. Planet ini memiliki pabrik musik tempat semua musik di alam semesta berasal dan diproduksi secara terus menerus melalui gelembung. Jika musik yang diproduksi oleh pabrik terhenti, waktu di Jammbo juga akan terhenti sehingga menyebabkan karakter terhenti. Setiap episode menampilkan plot di mana satu karakter atau beberapa karakter mempelajari pelajaran yang dapat dipelajari oleh pemirsa, dan menampilkan lagu sisipan yang mungkin bersifat instrumental atau vokal.

programme.title: Jelly Jamm S1, Ep 40
programme.desc: Jelly Jamm takes place on a fictional, colourful planet called Jammbo, following the adventures of seven characters: Bello, Goomo, Rita, Mina, Ongo, the King, and the Queen, who live in a small neighbourhood there. The planet has a music factory where all of the music in the universe originates from and is produced continuously through bubbles. If the music produced by the factory had stopped, time on Jammbo would also stop, causing the characters to freeze. Each episode features a plot in which a character or multiple characters learn a teachable lesson which the viewers can learn from, and features an insert song which may be instrumental or vocal.

programme.title: Jelly Jamm S1, Ep 40
programme.desc: Jelly Jamm terjadi di planet fiksi penuh warna bernama Jammbo, mengikuti petualangan tujuh karakter: Bello, Goomo, Rita, Mina, Ongo, Raja, dan Ratu, yang tinggal di lingkungan kecil di sana. Planet ini memiliki pabrik musik tempat semua musik di alam semesta berasal dan diproduksi secara terus menerus melalui gelembung. Jika musik yang diproduksi oleh pabrik terhenti, waktu di Jammbo juga akan terhenti sehingga menyebabkan karakter terhenti. Setiap episode menampilkan plot di mana satu karakter atau beberapa karakter mempelajari pelajaran yang dapat dipelajari oleh pemirsa, dan menampilkan lagu sisipan yang mungkin bersifat instrumental atau vokal.
